ode during checkout when buying the new piece you would like, and use the return authorization to send the original piece back to us.<br>                                Our team is always glad by to assist you with any questions you may have about your orders - feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:info@vaskia.com">info@vaskia.com.</a> Please provide your order confirmation number on the subject of your e-mail, and the nature of your correspondence, so we can assist you as quickly as humanly possible.                                 </span>                            </div>                        </div>                    </div>                    <div class="panel panel-default">                        <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingFourteen">                            <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFourteen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFourteen">                            14. How can I return my purchase?                            </a>                        </div>                        <div id="collapseFourteen" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingFourteen">                            <div class="panel-body">                            <span>In order to return your purchase you will have to contact our team at <a href="mailto:info@vaskia.com">info@vaskia.com</a> with your order number, product, and reason for return. We will review your request and send a return authorization once approved, and reimburse the amount to the account used during purchase.                             <br>                            Items must be returned in original condition and packaging.                            <br>                            Return shipping will be free for costumers within the US.                            <br>                            For returns outside the US, the buyer is liable for shipping costs.                            </span>                            </div>                        </div>                    </div>                    <div class="panel panel-default">                        <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingFifteen">                            <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFifteen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFifteen">                            15. Can I buy a gift card?                            </a>                        </div>                        <div id="collapseFifteen" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingFifteen">                            <div class="panel-body">                            <span>By all means, yes! This is actually one of the best presents a person can get. Go to our Brilliant Gifts section, and choose the gift card with the amount you would like to give.</span>                            </div>                        </div>                    </div>                </div>                         </div>        </div>            </div></div>